Class Admin

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.ingegneria.entities.Person
      • it.unipr.ingegneria.entities.Admin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOperations<Activity>, IOperationsPrevileged<Person,Activity>, IRandom<Person,Activity>

    public class Admin
extends Person
implements IOperationsPrevileged<Person,Activity>, IRandom<Person,Activity>
    The Admin class manage the operations inside the circle. Extends the abstract class Person and implement IOperationsPrevileged<T,C> interface.
    Author:
    Ruslan, Francesca, Nick
